00:01:18.405 --> 00:01:21.700
so we can have a good size
group and a discussion.

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:29.129
I just want to say a little bit
about Redleaf.

00:01:29.129 --> 00:01:36.475
He founded Whitebox Advisors in
